#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:2
msgid "JNDI"
msgstr "JNDI"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:6
msgid ""
"JNDI(Java Naming and Directory "
"Interface，Java命名和目录接口)是为Java应用程序提供命名和目录访问服务的API，允许客户端通过名称发现和查找数据、对象，用于提供基于配置的动态调用。这些对象可以存储在不同的命名或目录服务中，例如RMI、CORBA、LDAP、DNS等。"
msgstr ""
"JNDI (Java Naming and Directory Interface) is an API that provides naming "
"and directory access services for Java applications. It allows clients to "
"discover and look up data and objects by name, enabling configuration-based "
"dynamic invocation. These objects can be stored in different naming or "
"directory services, such as RMI, CORBA, LDAP, and DNS."

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:8
msgid ""
"其中Naming Service类似于哈希表的K/V对，通过名称去获取对应的服务。Directory Service是一种特殊的Naming "
"Service，用类似目录的方式来存取服务。"
msgstr ""
"A Naming Service is similar to K/V pairs in a hash table: the corresponding "
"service is obtained by name. A Directory Service is a special type of Naming "
"Service that accesses services in a directory-like manner."

