#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:14
msgid ""
"JNDI注入是2016年由pentester在BlackHat USA上的 ``A Journey From JNDI LDAP "
"Manipulation To RCE`` 议题提出的。"
msgstr ""
"JNDI injection was introduced by pentesters at Black Hat USA 2016 in the "
"talk ``A Journey From JNDI LDAP Manipulation To RCE``."

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:16
msgid "其攻击过程如下"
msgstr "The attack process is as follows"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:18
msgid "攻击者将Payload绑定到攻击者的命名/目录服务中"
msgstr "The attacker binds the Payload to the attacker's naming or directory service"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:19
msgid "攻击者将绝对URL注入易受攻击的JNDI查找方法"
msgstr "The attacker injects an absolute URL into a vulnerable JNDI lookup method"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:20
msgid "应用程序执行查找"
msgstr "The application performs the lookup"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:21
msgid "应用程序连接到攻击者控制的JNDI服务并返回Payload"
msgstr "The application connects to the attacker-controlled JNDI service and returns the Payload"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:22
msgid "应用程序解码响应并触发有效负载"
msgstr "The application decodes the response and triggers the payload"

