#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:38
msgid "RMI Remote Object"
msgstr "RMI Remote Object"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:39
msgid ""
"攻击者实现一个RMI恶意远程对象并绑定到RMI "
"Registry上，将编译后的RMI远程对象类放在HTTP/FTP/SMB等服务器上。其中Codebase地址由远程服务器的 "
"``java.rmi.server.codebase`` 属性设置，供受害者的RMI客户端远程加载。"
msgstr ""
"The attacker implements a malicious RMI remote object and binds it to the "
"RMI Registry, then places the compiled RMI remote object class on a server "
"such as HTTP, FTP, or SMB. The Codebase address is set by the remote "
"server's ``java.rmi.server.codebase`` property for remote loading by the "
"victim's RMI client."

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:41
msgid "利用条件如下："
msgstr "The exploitation conditions are as follows:"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:43
msgid "RMI客户端的上下文环境允许访问远程Codebase。"
msgstr "The RMI client's context environment allows access to the remote Codebase."

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:44
msgid "属性 ``java.rmi.server.useCodebaseOnly`` 的值为false。"
msgstr "The value of the ``java.rmi.server.useCodebaseOnly`` property is false."

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:46
msgid "其中JDK 6u45、7u21后，``java.rmi.server.useCodebaseOnly`` 的值默认为true。"
msgstr "After JDK 6u45 and 7u21, the value of ``java.rmi.server.useCodebaseOnly`` defaults to true."

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:49
msgid "RMI + JNDI Reference"
msgstr "RMI + JNDI Reference"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:50
msgid ""
"攻击者通过RMI服务返回一个JNDI Naming "
"Reference，受害者解码Reference时会去攻击者指定的远程地址加载Factory类。这种方式原理上并非使用RMI Class "
"Loading机制，因此不受 ``java.rmi.server.useCodebaseOnly`` 系统属性的限制。但是在JDK 6u132, "
"JDK 7u122, JDK 8u113 后限制了Naming/Directory服务中JNDI Reference远程加载Object "
"Factory类的特性。系统属性 ``com.sun.jndi.rmi.object.trustURLCodebase`` 、 "
"``com.sun.jndi.cosnaming.object.trustURLCodebase`` "
"的默认值变为false，即默认不允许从远程的Codebase加载Reference工厂类。"
msgstr ""
"The attacker uses an RMI service to return a JNDI Naming Reference. When the "
"victim decodes the Reference, it loads the Factory class from the remote "
"address specified by the attacker. In principle, this method does not use "
"the RMI Class Loading mechanism, so it is not restricted by the "
"``java.rmi.server.useCodebaseOnly`` system property. However, after JDK "
"6u132, JDK 7u122, and JDK 8u113, the feature that allows Naming/Directory "
"services to remotely load Object Factory classes through JNDI Reference was "
"restricted. The default values of the system properties "
"``com.sun.jndi.rmi.object.trustURLCodebase`` and "
"``com.sun.jndi.cosnaming.object.trustURLCodebase`` were changed to false, "
"meaning Reference factory classes are not allowed to be loaded from a remote "
"Codebase by default."

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:53
msgid "LDAP + JNDI Reference"
msgstr "LDAP + JNDI Reference"

#: ../../source/language/java/jndi.rst:54
msgid ""
"Java的LDAP可以在属性值中存储特定的Java对象，且LDAP服务的Reference远程加载Factory类不受 "
"``com.sun.jndi.rmi.object.trustURLCodebase`` "
"、``com.sun.jndi.cosnaming.object.trustURLCodebase`` 等属性的限制，适用范围更广。"
msgstr ""
"Java LDAP can store specific Java objects in attribute values, and remote "
"loading of Factory classes through LDAP service References is not restricted "
"by properties such as ``com.sun.jndi.rmi.object.trustURLCodebase`` and "
"``com.sun.jndi.cosnaming.object.trustURLCodebase``, so it applies in a "
"broader range of cases."
